<br>
<br>
To change your chat font size<br>
<br>
/chantfontsize &lt;#&gt;<br>
<br>
<br>
The Alternate windows are described in the text file.  You copy them into the directory you have my UI in if you want to change something.  Someone with mana will want to copy the contents of CasterPlayerWindow into their mod directory... someone who wants a pet box will need to copy PetInfoWindow.xml from their Default directory into the directory my mod's in.<br>
<br>
<br>
For those of you having problems loading the windows:<br>
<br>
This mod was MADE in 1024x768 for starters.  It won't look good in lower resolutions.<br>
<br>
If you load a skin like this:<br>
<br>
/LOADSKIN &lt;directory name&gt; 1<br>
<br>
It will load the skin and use the window location settings you already had.  If you leave the &quot;1&quot; off the end they'll load up very badly. <p><I>"Ohhh give me a home, where the Drolvarg don't roam... where the Tsu and the Urd Shamen play... Where seldom I'm trained, cuz I'm always feigned... and the Frenzy drops sashes alll dayyyyy...."</I> -Me, hugging dirt in PoF. <BR>
