-If you hold left click over one of the inventory slots in the &quot;Quick Inventory Box&quot;, you'll crash to desktop.  Basically, that window isn't coded to &quot;peel away&quot; a hotkey the way your full inventory window is.  So, please refrain from trying to pull hotkeys off that little window.  You'll crash every time.  I'll see if there's a possible fix.<br>
<br>
-People have also reported having problems with my BazaarWindow.xml.  If you try to use my Bazaar window in a lower resolution than 1024x768 you wont be able to see the bottom of the scroll bar.  If this happens to you, simply copy .\everquest\uifiles\defaul\BazaarWindow.xml  into the directory you have my mod in.<br>
<br>
